      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i'm having a major issue with some silk charmeuse. i'm sewing a bias-cut skirt and the seams keep puckering even though i'm using a very fine needle and my tension seems okay. any idea why it keeps bunching up like that?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
