    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i checked the seam allowance and it does seem to be getting a bit tight towards the hips. i've also tried adjusting the tension on the machine but it doesn't stop the fabric from looking all wavy/bunched up in those specific spots. is there anything else it could be? maybe something with the thread or the way the fabric is moving through the machine?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
