    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's weird because it's not even like the thread is breaking, it just feels like there's something constanty snagging or pulling at the fabric from underneath as it goes through, almost like something is catching it. i even tried using a walking foot but it didn't really help. is there any chance it's something with the feed dogs or how the fabric is being gripped?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
